    title: null,
    displayTitle: "9.9.25",
    lines: ["It is September 9th,","A sunny, green day at the end of summer.","The train is full but still.","","It is Tuesday, September 9th.","I’m reminded how the days near closer to winter,","In the chill on the train,","In the dew on the ground,","And in the mourning.","","The mourning.","I think about it,","In the morning,","When the cold creeps","Under my sheets and Creeps","Creep on the streets and","Each day passes with something to lose.","","It is Tuesday, September 9th, 2025,","A dark black tunnel descends into earth.","The hestic glow funnels from the hearth,","The pesty groans escape the throat,","I tredge the cape beyond the boat.","","It is today.","Today is today.","Today is a sunny green day in September,","And the dew traces my footprints."]
